 ُمُعَةِ فَاسْعَوْا إِلَىٰ ذِكْرِ اللَّه
 ِ\nO you who believe! When the call to prayer is made on Friday\,\nhasten
  to the remembrance of Allah. (62:9)\n\n• Perform ghusl (ritual bath)\n
